The Vitreous warped Jelly is the superior variant of Warped Jellies. It has a 1/200 chance of spawning while on a Slayer task of jellies after purchasing the unlock Bigger and Badder for 150 Slayer reward points from any Slayer master.

Drops[edit | edit source]

In addition to 100% drops and tertiary drops, superior slayer monsters will always roll 3 additional items, of which only 1 roll may be from the superior unique table. The other rolls are performed on the regular counterpart's table; their displayed drop chances represent a single roll.

Drop rates estimated based on 260,160 kills from the Drop Rate Project, unless otherwise cited.

The average Vitreous warped Jelly kill is worth 59,627.56.

The average Vitreous warped Jelly kill while on a Konar task is worth 61,652.29.
